{"tid":728050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國防部正研究 空中回收小型無人機","createTime":"2018-07-03T13:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T13:19:52.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5c0dd3d96e4d5538bdc5ed3a91c91704daaef1","tid":728050,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/211344_2c94d19b44b6a776643e1ba0a2e24bd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F211344_2c94d19b44b6a776643e1ba0a2e24bd5.png&h=7ed3602a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部正研回收小型無人機<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122513533/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%AD%A3%E7%A0%94%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122513533%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%2598%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A0%2594%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F&d=6m%2B4ZZmx8ZhvV5Z5sBxDQG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=283bc592\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F122513533%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%2580%259A%25E8%25AD%2598%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%2583%25A8%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A0%2594%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A9%259F&h=9ec740fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/122513533/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%80%9A%E8%AD%98/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%83%A8%E6%AD%A3%E7%A0%94%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E5%B0%8F%E5%9E%8B%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E6%A9%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n軍事無人機其中一個發展方向是低成本兼小型化，可以成群出動，不過由於回收困難，小型無人機通常都是用完即棄。不過美國國防部正研究一項技術，可以由大型軍機在空中回收小型無人機，有望大大提高軍用價值。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n轟炸機、戰鬥機及運輸機化身小型無人機的空中母艦，在空中連續發射多架小精靈無人機，讓一眾能避開敵軍掃描的小精靈，執行收集情報、監視及偵察等前線任務。行動完成後，他們就會回到運輸機底下與運輸機的拖索對接，之後關上電源，回到運輸機內。同時運輸機內的工作人員亦會進行一系列安全檢查，確保情況安全才進行回收，這個回收無人機的方法其實是借用空中加油技術，讓無人機能夠循環再用，大大節省軍事開支。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n每架小精靈無人機預計可以重覆使用二十次，每次回收後，只要進行小修補，二十四小時後又可以再次出動。小型無人機編隊能夠在空中出動及回收，意味軍方發射軍用無人機，不用再依賴陸上基地及航空母艦，由於根本不需要著陸，無人機甚至可以剔除傳統的起落架，令結構更輕巧，可以更高速飛行。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n美國國防部已經就這項計劃批出價值約三千九百萬美元的開發合約，正進行一系列地面和空中測試，預計明年底會嘗試在C-130 運輸機中發射、回收及修補多架無人機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e0/United_States_Department_of_Defense_Seal.svg/481px-United_States_Department_of_Defense_Seal.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fe%2Fe0%2FUnited_States_Department_of_Defense_Seal.svg%2F481px-United_States_Department_of_Defense_Seal.svg.png&h=183bb74a&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}